%Tutorial - DAY - Tables Services ----------------------------------------------
+  This function allows you to create (or modify) and display the WEEKDAY and
+  MONTH names tables.
+  N.B. - The WEEKDAY and MONTH names tables are members stored in the data-set
+         allocated to your session by the DD-name "ISPTLIB". The names of
+         these members are generated with the fixed prefix "TWKD" (WEEKDAY)
+         or "TMTH" (MONTH) and the suffix you have supplied at creation.
+  Depress%PF3+or%PF15+to return to the%DAY Services+panel.
)END
